      title="How to add LaTeX equations in Luna blog posts"
      date="22 Mar, 2025"
      description="Learn how to add LaTeX equations in Luna using Markdown, KaTeX, and remark/rehype plugins."
    />
    <PostCard
      title="Dynamic OG image generation in Luna"
      date="12 Mar, 2025"
      description="New feature in Luna v1.4.0, introducing dynamic OG image generation for blog posts."
    />
